OL,3,CPensioners left frustrated over lack
OL,4,Cof decision on alleged 'double tax'
OL,6,F"At pensionable age, such pensions
OL,7,Freceived are again liable to tax. This
OL,8,Famounts to double taxation and such
OL,9,Fpensions should be exempt from
OL,10,Ftaxation."
OL,12,FIn its original response, the States
OL,13,Fresponded that even though the old age
OL,14,Fpension is taxable, pensioners on low
OL,15,Fincomes who receive only the old age
OL,16,Fpension do not pay any income tax,
OL,17,Fadding that making the States old age
OL,18,Fpension exempt from tax would not
OL,19,Fbenefit pensioners with the lowest
OL,20,Fincomes.
