OL,3,CPensioners left frustrated over lack
OL,4,Cof decision on alleged 'double tax'
OL,6,FHowever, after being debated in the
OL,7,FState Assembly, pensioners were left
OL,8,Fannoyed that there was no vote on the
OL,9,Ftaxation and no clear signs that
OL,10,Fchange would be enacted.
OL,12,FPaul Troalic, who started the
OL,13,Fpetition, says: "I'm a little bit
OL,14,Fdisappointed, if I'm honest, because I
OL,15,Fthought with the number of signatures
OL,16,Fthat we had, they would take it a
OL,17,Flittle more seriously."
OL,19,FAnother pensioner quips: "It's an
OL,20,Fabsolutely crazy situation, but in all
OL,21,Ffairness, when do the States listen?"
