OL,3,CPensioners left frustrated over lack
OL,4,Cof decision on alleged 'double tax'
OL,6,FJersey Ministers have insisted that
OL,7,Fpensioners are not double-taxed.
OL,9,FThere are also concerns that stopping
OL,10,Fthe state pension from counting
OL,11,Ftowards people's taxable income would
OL,12,Fcost the government #21 million in
OL,13,Flost revenue annually.
OL,15,FHowever, there are also calls to how
OL,16,Fpetitions are treated when they reach
OL,17,Fthe threshold to be debated.
